{ White consolidated the position. Black should play  15...Ke8  16.Nd2  and sacrifice the piece back with  16...Nxc5  17.bxc5  Bxc5  when after  18.Qa4+  Kf8  19.Kf2  White has a pawn-up with little compensation for Black. }
