[SetUp "1"]

{ What prophylactic idea do we have to hinder our opponent's development? } 6.
e6
{ An important prophylactic idea in the course. We immediately shut down the dark-squared bishop. We don't want to play the popular  6.h4  h5  7.e6  Qd6  when Black is threatening ...Qg3+ and White struggles. }
