[SetUp "1"]

{ What prophylactic idea do we have here? } 10. h4
{ A fantastic prophylactic move. The idea is that after  10...Nxe5  11.Nxe5  Rxe5  12.Qd4  Rh5  , we prevent Black from playing ...Rh4. }
10... Nxe5 11. Nxe5 Rxe5 12. Qd4
{ Looks very good for White. After  12...Rh5  , we develop with tempo with  13.Be2!  We are happy that we played h4 now, preventing ...Rh4. As we studied, Black is now forced to sacrifice the rook with @@StartFEN@@r2qkbn1/pp1b1pp1/4p3/2Ppr3/3Q3P/2N1B3/PPP2P2/R3KB1R b KQq - 1 3@@EndFEN@@  12...Rxe3  covered here. }
